api_list.name: fixtures rounds
api_list.description:
Get the rounds for a league or a cup
**Update Frequency** : Every day
**Recommended Calls** : 1 call per day

api_list.name: players fixtures statistics
api_list.description:
Get the players statistics from one fixture
**Update Frequency** : Every minute
**Recommended Calls** : 1 call every minute for the fixtures in progress otherwise 1 call per day

api_list.name: seasons for players
api_list.description:
Get all available seasons for players statistics
**Update Frequency** : Every day
**Recommended Calls** : 1 call per day
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://api-football-beta.p.rapidapi.com/players/seasons"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "api-football-beta.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

optional_parameters.description: Fails if field is not a result of the endpoint timezone
